cerpt":"本人看了3-4遍大明王朝1566，但是对于一开始的毁堤淹田还是有疑问。从电视剧呈现的剧情看，严嵩事先是不知道毁堤淹田的，是小阁老伙同鄢懋卿罗龙文给郑何下的任务。严嵩都不知道(即使猜到明面上也是不知道)，说明这事不是严党和万寿帝君合谋的，自上而下的任务。万寿帝君和吕方后续知道这个，是杨金水干了毁堤淹田后，上报给吕方的，包括给李玄挪个职位。那杨金水为什么要参与谋划毁堤淹田呢，他自己说的他归宫里管，让地方官员自己踹被窝去。急递是严世蕃下给郑何的，他完全可以啥都不管，毁了田让沈一石去收田就完事了。这一波操作，后续让胡宗宪掣肘，又被海瑞翻出来审，以杨公公的精明，和做事的谨慎不该犯这个错。是我找到的为数不多的剧情bug吗？"},"attached_info":"CkEI9r/n+MqQk68BEAMaCTExMjE0Njc3NSCyubu6BjAAOMEBQBFyCjU4NTA4NzM0NzV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"44 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/9d387e8c357288c02f1a1994fbeba39c_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1736432303.528199","card_id":"Q_4655109637","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":4655109637,"title":"以投资为生的人是如何生存下来的？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/4655109637","type":"question","created":1732085484,"answer_count":30,"follower_count":60,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[395,1537,12585,19800,1833036],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAI9r/n+MqQk68BEAMaCTExMTkwNzY4OCDsjfa5BjAAODxAEnIKNDY1NTEwOTYzN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"44 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-73543af44d9e8fff30a5f368db7e5be1_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1736432303.528459","card_id":"Q_561523336","target":{"id":561523336,"title":"明朝为什么没有走殖民扩张的道路？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/561523336","type":"question","created":1666425563,"answer_count":27,"follower_count":62,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"